node.text: Go "Against the Grain" with our veggie burger! Black beans, brown rice, mac nuts, carrots, herbs, and flax make up this tasty sando, then topped with avocado, pickled ginger, and vegan mayo. Add a side of fries and a pint of beer for a well-rounded meal. 😋 🍺

node.text:
🍴 New Specials! 🍴 Head into #MBCKihei, #MBCWaikiki, or #MBCKailua to try these new limited-time dishes!

🦐 Shrimp & Sweet Corn Quesadilla 🦐
Crispy quesadilla, stuffed with shrimp, sweet corn, jalapeño, cilantro, cheddar and pepper jack cheeses. Served with sides of guacamole, sour cream and pico de gallo. 

🐖 Guava Pork Sliders with Baja Slaw 🐖 
Slow cooked and smoky Kalua-style shredded pork, glazed with our housemade Guava BBQ sauce – piled hot on slider buns with creamy slaw, pickles and crispy fried onions.

node.text: New Limited Canned Release! 🍊 A tribute to Hawaii’s favorite juice, POG Hazy IPA is loaded with locally sourced passion fruit, orange, and guava. Huell Melon, Southern Cross, and Citra hops bring delicate notes of grapefruit and melon for a very juicy beer. 🍺 Available locally and in select mainland markets.
